* Iron Raptor nodded as she heard Hot Rod speak, nodding towards him and 
then looking towards Prowler with a smile as Hot Rod motioned towards him.*

" Well, a new bot to the Maximal force is always welcome."

* She walked up towards Prowler, patting Hot Rod on the Arm.*

" Thanx for bringing him in Hot Rod."

* Iron Raptor then came up in front of Prowler and held out her hand for him 
to shake.*

" Hello, Prowler. And welcome to the Maximals."
